Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:57.74,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う毎日が　増えてゆくけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:07.65,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}お互いの気持ちはいつも　側にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:17.39,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ふたり会えなくても　平気だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:27.09,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強がり言うけど　溜め息まじりね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:37.47,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}過ぎてゆく季節に　置いてきた宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:42.29,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大切なピースの…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:57.74,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦肩而过的日子  总是在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:07.65,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}两人的想法却不会变  就在彼此身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:17.39,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算不能相见  也毫不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:27.09,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}逞强的话语里  却藏着叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:37.47,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}藏在逝去季节里的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:42.29,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是缺少的一片…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服饰和小道具也要做？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是做不到就要写别的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…这种事不用去做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让大家看到我写的剧本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去做设计
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我…做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  美咲  那样的话就得努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有构思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有…基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…本来也没打算画成图
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就先那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照构思一点点做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花点时间的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离最后彩排只剩两星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒过来推算一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备材料和实际动手…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起做大概会花多少时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  设计的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构思只在美咲的脑中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有美咲才能画出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的是很过分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在做什么啊  和小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会痛苦很正常  是那帮人太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了  真的对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油试试的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好的话可以帮我看下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次让我听听意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起剧本更能提出点好的意见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…白天的时候对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审查的时间突然提早了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听我说这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是筱冢  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗  美咲和田丸的那事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前年？  我们不是还没入学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是入学了还不得闹个天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团的那些学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是去年开始吧  就不怎么来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  我也没多少和你在学校里遇见的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为美咲一直很正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是在逞强  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在在意我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是…成熟的表现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又为什么对那样的美咲置之不理？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底都做了什么  彰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…很在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是如此吧  毕竟你在和那邻家女孩交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  比如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年和由绮见面的时候仅仅…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候她还没有出道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把教授牵扯进来  在系里造成了大骚动是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是第二件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四件  最后美咲还是拒绝了田丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田丸觉得那是对他的羞辱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对准备退出戏剧部的美咲说不需要退出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没让她退出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意让她不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她成了强制幽灵部员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼做些别人不做的杂务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪美咲会这样想不开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟放过这次机会的话  就没下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经没关系了吧  她和那个叫田丸的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田丸现在的女朋友是今年刚进来的部员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那样就好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服饰和小道具都做出来的话就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真像漫画里的主人公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行  昨天也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多余的话…别说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  整体过一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  …
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  脑子有点混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去你那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的预定是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在车上等您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…筱冢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  没想到你能忍到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没意义的  这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么要不要的  再说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看一…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事啦  只是睡眠不足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡就行了吧？也没其它的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得醒醒神才行  难得让你给我评价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以先睡着  我会自己看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶喝完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑咖啡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦藤井君  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害  太厉害了美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  由绮？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君  嗯…  现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全…没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在睡觉？还是有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  前不久跟彰他们玩太疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居变得很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  所以啊那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了的事啊  还有那奇怪的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车里偶然看到遥就赶忙写下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得让她看懂了不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是冬弥君也看不懂的话就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看懂了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是呢  去不了真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那只是我的任性而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨天开始我就在录新曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉非常紧张  想让你分我一点勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  马上就能录完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是最后的休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我给你打过一次电话的  你出去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我回了趟家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸的身体稍有不适
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲病了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是他的老病恶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一把年纪了真拿那老头没办法  虽然跟年龄无关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你没有勉强自己过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里出了那么大的事  要是你还来的话  我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以说没什么大事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  是  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再给你电话的  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说钢铁五社遭受了战后最大的赤字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候才应该把待遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藤井君  是给藤井君打电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎很忙  完全联系不上所以我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没跟他约好见面或者是去哪玩  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  那么再来一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了  说明会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说就用这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过了？很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面要怎么办呢  我完全没考虑过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢  去买材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧  在电话里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？你一人不可能做到吧  只剩两周了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:17:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道我能帮上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能这么向你撒娇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得找个帮手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮手吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥就不用问了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把彰拉来怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧  他说是今年倍受关注  要上演节目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了听说了  是要重现著名推理小说的事件现场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰太一本正经了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说只有我们两人而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很看好你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是看看布料  板子之类的材料就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的话不可能完成的  帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话是这样说  果然用脚来运还是有限度的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  开我家的车出来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的技术没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马马虎虎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  空白期多长了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是用脚运吧  才不要坐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  看我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  那个餐具  用得上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃饭那个场景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  非常精简
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且感觉不到特定的时代和地点  不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是由绮？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  全都不行  完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  她已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就用剪辑…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后有什么安排？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就继续吧  直到完成为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前线慰问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:29.14,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（夕凪大学设计同好会）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看这状况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很抱歉  不过不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在角落里就行了  能不能借用一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  可以的话借我一台缝纫机…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这种好事啊  泽仓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这时期了  还想一个人插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算是演剧部的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不可能了  到今天才突然过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各社团不都事先提出活动预定的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲  去借部室啊练习场之类的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉江  能来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七页  印象必须不断加深
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它会从开端慢慢崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.79,0:24:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album
